sequenceDiagram
    actor SecOfficer as Security Officer
    participant Dashboard
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant ReID as Person Re-ID Module
    participant Detection as Detection Engine
    participant Tracking as Tracking Module
    participant Camera as Camera Feeds
    participant Alert as Alert System
    participant Storage as Storage System
    
    SecOfficer->>Dashboard: Upload Reference Image
    Dashboard->>API: POST /person-search/start
    API->>ReID: Extract Person Embedding
    ReID->>ReID: Process Image (512-dim vector)
    ReID-->>API: Return Embedding Vector
    API->>Storage: Save Search Session
    API-->>Dashboard: Search Session Created
    Dashboard-->>SecOfficer: Display "Search Active"
    
    loop For Each Active Camera
        Camera->>Detection: Stream Video Frames
        Detection->>Detection: Detect Persons in Frame
        Detection->>ReID: Extract Embeddings for Detected Persons
        ReID->>ReID: Compute Cosine Similarity
        
        alt Similarity > Threshold (0.70)
            ReID->>Tracking: Match Found - Start Tracking
            Tracking->>Tracking: Assign Unique ID
            Tracking->>API: Report Match with Location
            API->>Storage: Log Match Event
            API->>Alert: Trigger Match Notification
            
            par Send Notifications
                Alert->>SecOfficer: WhatsApp Alert with Snapshot
                Alert->>Dashboard: Real-time Update
            end
            
            Dashboard-->>SecOfficer: Show Match Location on Map
            
            loop Track Across Cameras
                Camera->>Detection: New Frame from Different Camera
                Detection->>Tracking: Detected Person
                Tracking->>Tracking: Match to Existing ID
                Tracking->>API: Update Trajectory
                API->>Dashboard: Update Person Movement
                Dashboard-->>SecOfficer: Live Tracking Update
            end
        else No Match
            ReID->>API: No Match (Continue Scanning)
        end
    end
    
    SecOfficer->>Dashboard: Stop Search
    Dashboard->>API: POST /person-search/stop
    API->>Storage: Close Search Session
    API-->>Dashboard: Session Closed
    Dashboard-->>SecOfficer: Search Terminated